data.text:
Mark Protosevich (born August 24, 1961) is an American screenwriter currently under contract with Warner Bros.

Protosevich was born in Chicago, Illinois.

Filmography[]

The Cell (also producer)

Poseidon

I Am Legend

Thor

Jurassic Park IV

Mass Effect

He also wrote the script for the unproduced Batman Triumphant.

[]
